{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block body %}
    <div class="align-content-center">
        <div class="row m-3">
            <h1>Welcome to NailSaloon, where beauty meets precision!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="row m-3" id="short-description">
            <h2>
                Step into a world of glamour and pampering as we redefine the art of nail care. Our expert technicians
                are dedicated to enhancing your natural beauty and ensuring a delightful experience from the moment you
                walk through our doors.
            </h2>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div class="row m-3">
            <div>
                <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
            </div>
            <div>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        ✨ Expert Nail Technicians: Our highly skilled nail technicians are passionate about their craft,
                        bringing creativity and precision to every service. From classic manicures to trendy nail art,
                        we've got the expertise to make your nails a work of art.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        💅 Premium Products: We believe in using only the finest products to ensure the health and beauty
                        of your nails. Our selection of high-quality polishes, gels, and nail care products will leave
                        your nails looking stunning and feeling healthy.

                    </li>
                    <li>
                        🌟 Luxurious Atmosphere: Immerse yourself in a world of luxury and relaxation. Our salon is
                        designed to provide a serene and comfortable environment where you can unwind and indulge in
                        some well-deserved self-care.

                    </li>
                    <li>
                        🌈 Trendsetting Nail Art: Stay ahead of the trends with our innovative and customizable nail art
                        options. Whether you prefer chic minimalism or bold and vibrant designs, our artists will bring
                        your vision to life.

                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="row m-3">
                <div>
                    <h2>Services We Offer:</h2>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <ul>
                        <li>🔍 Manicures and Pedicures: Treat your hands and feet to the care they deserve with our rejuvenating manicure and pedicure services.
                        </li>
                        <li>💅 Nail Extensions: Achieve the perfect length and shape with our high-quality nail extensions for a glamorous and polished look.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            🌸 Nail Art and Design: Express your personality with our wide range of nail art options,
                            from intricate designs to minimalist elegance.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            💎 Gel and Acrylic Services: Enhance the durability and shine of your nails with our premium
                            gel and acrylic services.
                        </li>
                        <li> 👣 Foot Spa Treatments: Indulge in a luxurious foot spa experience that will leave you
                            feeling relaxed and rejuvenated.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
{% endblock %}
